devdoc.author: JustCause This is a proof of concept starter contract for lossless donations Aave v3 is used to generate interest for crowdfunding Contributors deposit tokens into JustCausePool which deposit them into Aave lending protocol. The interest earned is directed to the receiver associated with the Pool. When Contributors need access to their funds they withdraw original deposit and interest accrued is left behind for the receiver to claim.
devdoc.details: To be covered by a proxy contractdeposits, withdraws, withdrawDonations controlled by the PoolTracker contract (Master)*
